WorkItem.Description:
* implement a language service host and run your own language service
* have two files like this

```
declare class Animal {
	name:string;
}

interface Zoo {
	getAnimalByName(name:string):Animal;	
}

var zoo:Zoo;
```

```
zoo.getAnimalByName('tiger');
```
* edit the last line in the first file so that ```zoo``` becomes ```zooh```
* in the language service run a syntactic and semantic check for both files

-> you will not get an error in file #2
-> make an edit in file #2 (whitespace change) and see an error
